{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271530/extras/PTCLogo_Transparent_New.png?t=1733694364\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83c\udf7f Pop the Corn: Kernel Clicker \ud83c\udf7f</strong></h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Welcome to the tastiest clicker game around! Pop the Corn: Kernel Clicker is all about turning tiny kernels into a mountain of delicious, profitable popcorn, one satisfying pop at a time!</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">\ud83d\udd25 <strong>Pop 'til you drop:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Drop kernels into the pan and watch the magic happen</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Collect your popped treasures for cold, hard cash</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Upgrade your popping game to churn out popcorn faster than ever!</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83d\udcb0 Chase that golden dream:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Embrace the endorphins when you hear the jingle of the rarer golden popcorn</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Spend your hard-earned cash on shiny new pans</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Switch up your popping scenery with unlockable skies</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83c\udfb5 Unwind and relax:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Let the satisfying pop-pop-pop soothe your stress away!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Enjoy a calm, pressure-free gaming experience</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Perfect for unwinding after a long day or during short breaks</p></li></ul><h2 class=\"bb_tag\"><strong>\ud83c\udfc5 Pop and achieve at your pace:</strong></h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Tons of in-game and Steam achievements to unlock!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Challenge yourself with a variety of popcorn-popping goals</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">No rush, no pressure - just <i>pure</i> popcorn fun at your own pace, accompanied by some soothing jazzy tunes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pop the Corn: Kernel Clicker is your cosy corner in the gaming world. It's a small, fun game that's always satisfying to play, whether you've got five minutes or five hours. Let the rhythmic popping and gentle gameplay wash away your worries, and why not grab a bag of Popcorn to munch on as you play, because you deserve it! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><strong><i>Take it easy, and get popping!</i></strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3271530/extras/Pop.gif?t=1733694364\" /></p>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Pop it!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Pop it Hard","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Pop it Harder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Pop it... even harder","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Pop it like its hot","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Pop till you drop","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Top of the Pops","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/3271530/a67162b0fd496bbafd5c8f51f14c626c1510edd5.jpg"},{"name":"Popstar","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstat